ShipMonk: Streamlined 3PL Solutions for Seamless Fulfillment

Running a successful DTC ecommerce business is a wild ride! From managing inventory and processing orders to handling shipping and returns, there’s a lot to juggle. Drowning in the details? That’s where ShipMonk comes in. We’re a leading 3PL provider offering comprehensive ecommerce fulfillment solutions designed to help large enterprise brands optimize operations and explode your growth. We take the stress out of fulfillment so you can focus on building your brand and connecting with your customers.

Trusted by brands that are scaling with ease

What is 3PL fulfillment?

3PL fulfillment means outsourcing your ecommerce logistics operations to a specialized provider like ShipMonk. We handle everything from warehousing and inventory management to picking, packing, and shipping your orders. Think of us as your dedicated fulfillment team, working behind the scenes to keep your customers happy and your business booming.

Global fulfillment network for the fastest-click-to-delivery

ShipMonk’s global fulfillment network puts your inventory closer to your customers. With strategically located warehouses in the US, Canada, the U.K., and Mainland Europe, we can split your inventory and automatically select the optimal shipping location for every order. This means faster delivery, reduced shipping costs, and happier customers. We’re everywhere you need to be.

One platform, total fulfillment control

Omnichannel ecommerce management

We’re a tech-first company, and our platform is designed to empower your omnichannel success. Our custom warehouse management system (WMS), intelligent inventory management system (IMS) and order management system (OMS) work together to streamline your operations, providing you with the tools you need to manage inventory, track orders, optimize shipping, and integrate seamlessly with all your sales channels. Our proprietary technology puts you in control.

Auto-merge

Auto-combine unfulfilled orders for the same customer and save on fulfillment and shipping costs.

Backorder management

Erase ambiguity for your customers. Opt to wait for more inventory, split-ship, or alter the items in an order.

Branded tracking

Utilize our custom post-purchase tracking page as a place to boost brand awareness, drive promos, and repeat purchases.

Claims portal

Sometimes,shiphappens. ShipMonk lets you automatically file, track and resolve claims directly in-portal.

Lot control

Trace inventory by production lots and expiration, with vision back to specific customers and deliveries.

Serialization

Youll know exactly which unit of inventory is on your customers doorstep.

In-app batching

Create each unique box as a batch within the ShipMonk platform and assign orders to each batch.

Integrations

Integrate ShipMonk with any of our 100+ ecommerce shopping carts, marketplaces, and solution providers.

Maximize efficiency with smart automation

Scale your fulfillment with automation & technology

ShipMonk’s state-of-the-art fulfillment centers are designed for speed and efficiency. Our advanced automation and proprietary software work together seamlessly to process 100,000+ orders daily, ensuring lightning-fast fulfillment and exceptional accuracy. We’re talking serious fulfillment power!

Here's what you get:

Dimensional SKU scanning

Our advanced dimensional scanning process captures detailed product information weight, dimensions, and even photos. This data isn’t just stored; it’s used to optimize packaging, calculate accurate shipping rates, and improve overall fulfillment efficiency.

Smart storage auto slotting

ShipMonks intelligent auto-slotting optimizes storage by continuously monitoring SKU velocity and routing inventory to the most efficient warehouse locationsensuring faster picking and packing.

Automation

ShipMonk’s automated mobile robots are revolutionizing fulfillment. These tireless robots minimize pick times, speed up order processing, and ensure industry-leading accuracy. The result? Faster fulfillment, reduced costs, and happier customers.

Pick-to-light

ShipMonk’s pick-to-light technology streamlines your high-volume fulfillment. Our system uses LED lights to guide pickers to the exact location of each item, ensuring accuracy and efficiency, even with frequent replenishment.

Automated conveyors

Our fulfillment centers are equipped with state-of-the-art conveyor systems that optimize the flow of goods. From receiving to shipping, your products are transported quickly and efficiently, minimizing delays and maximizing productivity.

Automated sorting

ShipMonk’s automated sorting system accelerates your fulfillment. Packages are automatically sorted and routed to the correct bins for carrier pickup, ensuring faster processing and quicker delivery to your customers.
